00:11:30.500 --> 00:11:31.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu harika.

137
00:11:32.333 --> 00:11:33.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aynen bunu yaz.

138
00:11:34.041 --> 00:11:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"İyi ile kötü arasında ahlakî çelişki."

139
