Çok iyi Magne!

140
00:11:38.416 --> 00:11:39.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Merhaba Iman.
-Merhaba.

141
00:11:45.333 --> 00:11:46.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gözlük mü takıyorsun?

142
00:11:48.416 --> 00:11:50.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır. Bazen.

143
00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:55.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba Iman.

144
00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:57.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba Ada. N'aber?

145
00:11:57.500 --> 00:11:59.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İngilizce notları açıklanmış.

146
00:11:59.250 --> 00:12:01.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sadece not.

147
00:12:03.041 --> 00:12:05.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne? İngilizce "C" mi?

148
00:12:06.583 --> 00:12:07.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Akıcı konuşuyorum!

149
00:12:08.166 --> 00:12:11.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Büroda kimse var mı?
-Evet, Ran var.

150
00:12:17.541 --> 00:12:19.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Notlar tartışmaya açık değil Iman.

151
00:12:20.375 --> 00:12:24.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ailemin ne kadar üzüleceğini
anlıyorsunuzdur umarım.

152
00:12:24.291 --> 00:12:26.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Geçmişimi biliyorsunuz.

153
00:12:27.833 --> 00:12:29.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benden özel muamele istiyorsun,

154
00:12:29.833 --> 00:12:31.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
sırf kökenin…

155
00:12:33.166 --> 00:12:35.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sri Lanka mıydı?
-Sri Lanka.

156
00:12:35.125 --> 00:12:37.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Ben Norveçliyim.
-Beni anlıyorsun.

157
00:12:37.750 --> 00:12:40.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır, anlamıyorum.

158
00:12:40.791 --> 00:12:44.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sri Lanka kökenli olduğun için sana karşı

159
00:12:44.625 --> 00:12:48.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
özel muamele yapmamı
istiyor gibisin, diyorum.

160
00:12:48.416 --> 00:12:50.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunu yapmaya izniniz yok.

161
00:12:51.083 --> 00:12:52.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bence birinin kökenine göre

162
00:12:52.791 --> 00:12:55.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
not vermek yasa dışı.

163
00:13:03.208 --> 00:13:05.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Fakat bence tekrar düşününce

164
00:13:05.958 --> 00:13:08.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
çok iyi biliyorsunuz

165
00:13:09.958 --> 00:13:12.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İngilizcede C'yi hak etmediğimi.

166
00:13:14.208 --> 00:13:15.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ayrıca bana göre

167
00:13:17.375 --> 00:13:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
çok çekici bir kadınsınız.

168
00:13:21.666 --> 00:13:26.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
En çekici bulduğum şeyse

169
00:13:28.208 --> 00:13:29.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
görünüşe göre neredeyse

170
00:13:31.250 --> 00:13:33.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
daha incinir hâle gelmeniz.

171
00:13:37.208 --> 00:13:39.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Belki bunu daha çok benimsemelisiniz.

172
00:13:41.375 --> 00:13:42.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biraz rahatlamalısınız.

173
00:14:20.375 --> 00:14:23.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
SUYU İÇMEYİN!
ANNENİZ

174
00:14:23.541 --> 00:14:27.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
DUR - GİRİŞ YASAK

175
00:15:18.833 --> 00:15:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Laurits!

176
00:15:22.083 --> 00:15:25.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Daha önce belirttiğimiz gibi</i>
<i>Jutul Endüstrileri akıllıca davranıp</i>

177
00:15:25.958 --> 00:15:26.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
EDDA IZGARA

178
00:15:26.958 --> 00:15:30.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>genç çevre eylemcilerini</i>
<i>görüşmeye davet etti.</i>

179
00:15:30.958 --> 00:15:32.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
JUTUL
İKLİM KATİLLERİ

180
00:15:32.291 --> 00:15:35.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<i>Birkaç gün önce</i>
<i>gençler Jutul Endüstrilerine geldi</i>

181
00:15:35.541 --> 00:15:39.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
ve olay, sosyal medyaya da yansıdı.
Konuyla ilgili kargaşa çıktı.

182
00:15:39.125 --> 00:15:40.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kaç yaşındasın? 15 mi?

183
00:15:40.416 --> 00:15:42.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
16. Seni ilgilendirmez ama.

184
00:15:42.375 --> 00:15:44.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Ben yapmam.
-Evet.

185
00:15:44.791 --> 00:15:46.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Magne yapar.
-Herkes…

186
00:15:46.583 --> 00:15:50.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Magne mi? Etrafta bağrış çağrış
dolaşan eleman mı?

187
00:15:50.958 --> 00:15:52.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Dolaşan mı?
-Etrafta dolaşıyor.

188
00:15:52.916 --> 00:15:54.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sözcünüz o mu?

189
00:15:54.625 --> 00:15:56.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Çok tuhaf.
-Ne diyorsun?

190
00:15:56.916 --> 00:16:01.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Jutul Endüstrileriyle toplantıda
temsilcimiz kim olacak?

191
00:16:01.958 --> 00:16:04.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bence Magne olmalı. En mantıklı tercih.

192
00:16:04.416 --> 00:16:06.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hayır!
-Hep buradaydı.

193
00:16:06.125 --> 00:16:07.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Her şeyi o başlattı.

194
00:16:07.708 --> 00:16:10.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir kız olmalı dedik, değil mi?

195
00:16:10.583 --> 00:16:12.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Laurits yapabilir. Kız gibi giyinirsin.

196
00:16:16.250 --> 00:16:17.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır mı?

197
00:16:18.333 --> 00:16:20.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Laurits, bizimle oturmak ister misin?

198
00:16:21.000 --> 00:16:22.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İyi misin?

199
00:16:24.541 --> 00:16:25.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır mı?

200
00:16:25.791 --> 00:16:28.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet, o berbat günlerden biri.

201
00:16:28.708 --> 00:16:30.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Tamam.
-Kendimi birazcık evsiz gibi

202
00:16:32.083 --> 00:16:33.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
hissediyorum.

203
00:16:33.791 --> 00:16:34.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet, olay…

204
00:16:35.500 --> 00:16:38.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sütsüz, şekersiz, sade kahve.

205
00:16:42.083 --> 00:16:43.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kapımız sana her zaman açık.

206
00:16:47.000 --> 00:16:52.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Magne olmalı. Başka türlü nasıl…

207
00:17:24.625 --> 00:17:27.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Notuna itiraz mı ettin?
-Evet.

208
00:17:28.083 --> 00:17:29.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Meğerse hataymış.

209
00:17:31.458 --> 00:17:33.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
A aldım.

210
00:17:33.958 --> 00:17:34.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamam.

211
00:17:35.291 --> 00:17:37.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Notların düzelmeye mi başladı?

212
00:17:37.125 --> 00:17:40.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Evet. Birazcık
güçlerimi kullanmış olabilirim.

213
00:17:41.541 --> 00:17:43.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Bunu yapamazsın.
-Yaparım.

214
00:17:43.416 --> 00:17:44.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır, yapamazsın!

215
00:17:44.500 --> 00:17:46.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana ne ki?

216
00:17:46.083 --> 00:17:48.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeteneklerini böyle kullanamazsın.

217
00:17:48.416 --> 00:17:51.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeni giysiler ve iyi notlar için olmaz.

218
00:17:53.375 --> 00:17:55.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen bıraktın Magne.

219
00:17:56.166 --> 00:17:58.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bana nutuk çekme.

220
00:17:58.500 --> 00:18:00.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İstediğimi yaparım.

221
00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:18.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Selam. Konuşmalıyız.

222
00:18:20.541 --> 00:18:22.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Odanda iğrenç bir şey buldum.

223
00:18:24.291 --> 00:18:25.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne?

224
00:18:26.791 --> 00:18:29.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Odama mı girdin?
-Tabii ki.

225
00:18:29.166 --> 00:18:31.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kapıda bir not var galiba.

226
00:18:32.041 --> 00:18:35.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Çamaşırların yıkanıp ütülendiğinde
şikayet etmiyorsun ama.

227
00:18:35.708 --> 00:18:37.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oraya girme!

228
00:18:37.458 --> 00:18:39.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ninenin eski akvaryumundaki şey ne?

229
00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:41.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evcil hayvan.

230
00:18:41.666 --> 00:18:43.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evcil hayvan değil.

231
00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:44.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anne…

232
00:18:45.833 --> 00:18:51.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Herkes gibi tavşan
ya da şirin yavru köpekler sevmiyorum.

233
00:18:51.125 --> 00:18:53.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Giysilerim farklı,
dinlediğim müzik farklı.

234
00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:56.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Bu kültürün parçası olarak
sürüngenleri seviyorum.

235
00:18:56.958 --> 00:18:58.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O şey ne?

236
00:18:59.041 --> 00:19:03.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Irk, cinsel kimlik
ve normalliğe inanmıyorum.

237
00:19:03.958 --> 00:19:05.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O şey gidecek.

238
00:19:05.166 --> 00:19:06.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Ona ihtiyacım var.
-Niye?

239
00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:09.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Cinsel kimliğe inanmadığın için mi?

240
00:19:09.750 --> 00:19:12.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hayır, babamı yeni kaybettiğim için.

241
00:19:39.250 --> 00:19:42.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Normal hayatın tadını çıkarıyor musun?

242
00:19:45.000 --> 00:19:46.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey!

243
00:19:46.791 --> 00:19:48.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, serseri! Hey!

244
00:19:55.208 --> 00:19:57.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benzinimi mi çalıyorsun?

245
00:20:03.083 --> 00:20:04.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Üzgünüm.

246
00:20:06.875 --> 00:20:08.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anlamıştır artık Harry. Dur!

247
00:20:10.291 --> 00:20:12.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benim mekanım, benim kurallarım.

248
00:20:14.833 --> 00:20:17.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Annen almaya gelene dek
motor burada kalıyor!

249
00:20:19.458 --> 00:20:21.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yapıyorsun?

250
00:20:22.041 --> 00:20:25.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
20 kronluk benzin çaldı diye mi
onu dövdün?

251
00:20:26.125 --> 00:20:27.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Güçlerini böyle kullanamazsın.

252
00:20:29.458 --> 00:20:30.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen yoksun.

253
00:20:36.708 --> 00:20:37.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Siktir!

254
00:20:41.041 --> 00:20:46.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tatlım, fazladan jambon getirdim,
tabii o şey yiyorsa.

255
00:20:48.083 --> 00:20:48.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sağ ol.

256
00:20:50.541 --> 00:20:51.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir şey sorsam?

257
00:20:51.875 --> 00:20:53.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Madem bir erkeksin ya da bir…

258
00:20:53.666 --> 00:20:57.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Cinsiyet ya da cinselliği
bu şekilde kabul etmiyorsun ama…

259
00:20:58.541 --> 00:21:04.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Erik'e mesaj atıp benimle
akşam yemeği yer misin, diye sordum…

260
00:21:04.416 --> 00:21:08.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Dinle. "Kulağa hoş geliyor.
Nokta, nokta, nokta."

261
00:21:08.833 --> 00:21:10.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"Nokta, nokta, nokta" ne demek?

262
00:21:10.958 --> 00:21:13.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Alaycı mı? Yoksa olumlu mu?

263
00:21:14.958 --> 00:21:15.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

264
00:21:16.875 --> 00:21:20.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Anne, öğretmenimle flört etmene
yardımcı olamam. Acayip kaçıyor.

265
00:21:20.833 --> 00:21:22.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet, anlıyorum.

266
00:21:22.416 --> 00:21:24.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hepimiz buradayız. Yiyelim.

267
00:21:25.000 --> 00:21:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sonra yerim.
-Hayır Laurits. Hey.

268
00:21:48.958 --> 00:21:49.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

269
00:21:55.833 --> 00:21:57.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne diyeceğimi bilmiyorum.

270
00:21:59.500 --> 00:22:01.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biliyorum, bana kızgınsın.

271
00:22:03.250 --> 00:22:04.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benden nefret ediyorsun.

272
00:22:08.500 --> 00:22:10.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Olanlar için cidden üzgünüm.

273
00:22:13.125 --> 00:22:14.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şunu bilmeni istiyorum,

