00:25:24.416 --> 00:25:25.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Neler oluyor?

315
00:25:26.500 --> 00:25:27.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
