-Evet.

328
00:26:32.458 --> 00:26:34.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Neden?
-Gerekliydi.

329
00:26:34.750 --> 00:26:36.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vidar yapamadı.

330
00:26:36.625 --> 00:26:38.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O yaşlı hâliyle yumuşadı.

331
00:26:41.333 --> 00:26:42.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne oldu sana?

332
00:26:44.125 --> 00:26:46.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gitmeyecek miydin? Gry'le?

333
00:26:51.875 --> 00:26:53.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne oldu sana?

334
00:26:55.666 --> 00:26:59.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Vidar'ı öldürdün.
Bana başka seçenek bırakmadın.

335
00:27:09.708 --> 00:27:10.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tüm gücün bu mu?

336
00:27:11.875 --> 00:27:13.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hadi!

337
00:27:15.541 --> 00:27:16.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne oldu?

338
00:27:24.500 --> 00:27:26.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Gel buraya. Hadi.

339
00:27:35.416 --> 00:27:37.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey. Magne.

340
00:27:37.250 --> 00:27:39.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vidar bana güçlendiğini söylemişti.

341
00:27:41.916 --> 00:27:42.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Göster.

342
00:27:46.875 --> 00:27:48.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tüm gücün bu mu?

343
00:27:52.250 --> 00:27:53.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Güçlerin nerede?

344
00:27:54.583 --> 00:27:55.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Magne?

345
00:28:07.166 --> 00:28:08.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yine güçsüz mü oldun?

346
