Sen bir hiçsin.

347
00:28:24.041 --> 00:28:25.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Öldürmeye bile değmezsin.

348
00:29:01.291 --> 00:29:02.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

349
00:29:03.083 --> 00:29:04.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Torunun mu?

350
00:29:05.666 --> 00:29:06.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Öyle sayılır.

351
