363
00:30:42.916 --> 00:30:47.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seni köpek gibi tekmelediğinde?

364
00:30:49.958 --> 00:30:52.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yapmak istedin Magne?

365
00:30:59.333 --> 00:31:00.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beni zorlama.

366
00:31:01.625 --> 00:31:02.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Laurits ve ben

