00:32:31.375 --> 00:32:32.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mezardan baltayı aldın.

371
00:32:33.416 --> 00:32:34.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Artık benim.

372
00:32:38.666 --> 00:32:39.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İhtiyacımız yok gerçi.

373
00:32:40.583 --> 00:32:42.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
