iyi bence Saxa.

389
00:34:09.666 --> 00:34:10.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

390
00:34:11.666 --> 00:34:12.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merhaba.

391
00:34:22.666 --> 00:34:25.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Toplantıyı iptal etmişler, duydun mu?

392
00:34:27.958 --> 00:34:29.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Jutul.

393
