395
00:34:41.166 --> 00:34:43.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet, bu…

396
00:34:43.708 --> 00:34:45.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Merdivenden düştüm.

397
00:34:45.500 --> 00:34:46.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bakayım.

398
00:34:51.333 --> 00:34:52.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dokunma.

399
00:34:59.625 --> 00:35:01.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Savaşa hazırsındır umarım.

400
00:35:20.958 --> 00:35:22.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Vaktin var mı?

401
00:35:24.000 --> 00:35:25.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kardeşim.

402
00:35:26.708 --> 00:35:27.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
