00:36:54.625 --> 00:36:57.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kimse kendini dışlanmış hissetmemeli.

417
00:37:01.916 --> 00:37:06.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
