00:37:32.208 --> 00:37:33.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sağ ol.

421
00:37:41.208 --> 00:37:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Kuzey tanrıları yasa ve düzeni</i>
<i>temsil ediyordu,</i>

422
00:37:45.041 --> 00:37:46.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>devler ise kaosu.</i>

423
00:37:47.666 --> 00:37:49.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Viking dünyası basitti.</i>

424
00:37:49.166 --> 00:37:52.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Tanrıların devleri öldürmesi</i>
<i>kötülük olarak değil,</i>

425
00:37:54.125 --> 00:37:57.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>dünyada dengeyi korumak adına</i>
<i>zorunluluk kabul edilirdi.</i>

426
00:37:58.875 --> 00:38:04.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Kaosun güçleri çok artarsa</i>
<i>dünya son bulurdu.</i>

427
00:38:18.750 --> 00:38:19.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey.

428
00:38:20.708 --> 00:38:21.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yapıyorsun?

429
00:38:22.458 --> 00:38:26.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mezar taşı geldi, ben de bitiriyorum.

430
00:38:37.208 --> 00:38:41.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
"TEK YAPABİLECEĞİM KENDİM OLMAK."
BOB DYLAN

431
00:38:59.250 --> 00:39:00.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yardım etmemiz gerekmez mi?

432
00:39:01.500 --> 00:39:02.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Onlar halleder.

433
00:39:06.666 --> 00:39:08.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Mad Men </i>dizisindeki gibi.

434
00:39:10.916 --> 00:39:13.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
60'larda böyle mi görünüyordun?

435
00:39:17.791 --> 00:39:19.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Saxa sana ne önerdi?

436
00:39:20.333 --> 00:39:23.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Buraya gelip bu aile oyununa
katılman için?

437
00:39:25.625 --> 00:39:26.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oy hakkı.

438
00:39:27.958 --> 00:39:29.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hak ettiğim yeri.

439
00:39:32.333 --> 00:39:34.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bildiğin gibi kardeşim…

440
00:39:36.625 --> 00:39:38.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben bir devim,

441
00:39:39.666 --> 00:39:40.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
senin gibi.

442
00:39:49.083 --> 00:39:49.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Para mı?

443
00:39:52.500 --> 00:39:55.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Senin gibiler
her zaman parasızdır, değil mi?

444
00:39:58.250 --> 00:39:59.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nedenin bir parçası da o.

445
00:39:59.916 --> 00:40:03.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sorun şu ki Saxa sana hiçbir şey veremez.

446
00:40:04.708 --> 00:40:05.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben verebilirim.

447
00:40:07.291 --> 00:40:08.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sadık olduğun sürece.

448
00:40:10.791 --> 00:40:14.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Soru şu, bedelin ne?

449
00:40:17.458 --> 00:40:18.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok pahalıyım.

450
00:40:23.500 --> 00:40:24.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Değilsin.

451
00:40:30.250 --> 00:40:34.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hiçbir zaman bir şeyi olmamış birini
ikna etmek kolaydır Laurits.

452
00:40:40.166 --> 00:40:41.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne konuşuyorsunuz?

453
00:40:44.166 --> 00:40:46.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aramızda dünyayı bölüşüyoruz.

454
00:40:46.291 --> 00:40:48.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunu yaptık sanıyordum.

455
00:40:50.166 --> 00:40:51.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ama…

456
00:40:53.000 --> 00:40:55.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bölüşecek bir şeyin yok Saxa.

457
00:40:58.583 --> 00:40:59.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beni sınıyor musun?

458
00:41:05.833 --> 00:41:09.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Belki de ben devreye girmeden önce

459
00:41:10.750 --> 00:41:12.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
bu konuyu halletmelisiniz.

460
00:41:19.000 --> 00:41:20.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evine bırakayım.

461
00:41:32.750 --> 00:41:33.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok hoştu.

462
00:41:35.250 --> 00:41:37.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Son karşılaşmamızdan daha hoş.

463
00:41:38.208 --> 00:41:39.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sana karşı dürüstüm sadece.

464
00:41:40.958 --> 00:41:42.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Umarım anlıyorsundur.

465
00:41:44.416 --> 00:41:46.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Şunu da anla, seni her zaman

466
00:41:47.375 --> 00:41:49.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
sadece bir piç olarak göreceğim.

467
00:41:52.291 --> 00:41:53.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet.

468
00:41:57.958 --> 00:41:59.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Piç de olsa gerçek bir çocuk.

469
00:42:01.791 --> 00:42:03.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hiç çocuğun olmadı.

470
00:42:05.125 --> 00:42:07.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Saxa bana devleri anlattı ve…

471
00:42:09.333 --> 00:42:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sizlerin 3.000 yıl öncesinden kalma
dışlanmış,

472
00:42:12.166 --> 00:42:14.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
tanrı artıkları olduğunuzu.

473
00:42:16.875 --> 00:42:18.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Aile olayının bir numara olduğunu.

474
00:42:21.125 --> 00:42:22.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kısır olduğunuzu.

475
00:42:25.625 --> 00:42:27.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Görünüşe göre Vidar hariç.

476
00:42:33.041 --> 00:42:34.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ben de dürüst konuşuyorum.

477
00:42:35.500 --> 00:42:36.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Üvey anne.

478
00:42:44.500 --> 00:42:45.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hoşça kal.

479
00:43:01.916 --> 00:43:04.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Anne, jambon bitmiş.

480
00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:11.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Asla ailemin bir parçası olamazsın.

481
00:43:14.833 --> 00:43:16.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey, dur!

482
00:43:17.500 --> 00:43:20.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sen ve ben aynıyız.
Beni öldüremezsin. Uzak dur!

483
00:43:22.541 --> 00:43:24.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seni öldürmeye gelmedim.

484
00:43:24.833 --> 00:43:25.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Henüz.

485
00:43:41.125 --> 00:43:42.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bırak onu!

486
00:43:47.416 --> 00:43:48.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yapacaksın?

487
00:43:50.000 --> 00:43:51.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Güçlerin yok.

488
00:43:53.000 --> 00:43:54.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Olan gücümle savaşırım.

489
00:43:58.541 --> 00:44:01.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Güçlerin yokken
bizi tutabilecek bir engel yok.

490
00:44:02.416 --> 00:44:04.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen ve ailenin peşine düşeceğiz.

491
00:44:11.916 --> 00:44:13.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Selam!

492
00:44:14.083 --> 00:44:15.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kapı açık ve…

493
00:44:15.500 --> 00:44:18.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Misafirimiz mi var?
Okulda Magne'ye bir şey mi oldu?

494
00:44:18.625 --> 00:44:21.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Çocuklarla final sınavını
konuşmaya geldim.

495
00:44:21.666 --> 00:44:23.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Magne, düştün mü?

496
00:44:23.708 --> 00:44:28.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dondurma aldım. İstersen bolca var.

497
00:44:28.083 --> 00:44:30.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yok, ben de tam çıkıyordum…

498
00:44:30.750 --> 00:44:31.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Biraz sakarsın.

499
00:44:31.958 --> 00:44:33.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sizlerle konuşmak güzeldi.

500
00:44:43.250 --> 00:44:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İşte geliyor.

501
00:44:54.833 --> 00:44:55.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hazırsın.

502
00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:00.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Güçlerimi almama yardım et.

503
00:45:03.041 --> 00:45:04.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Thor'u tamamlayan neydi?

504
00:45:06.166 --> 00:45:07.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çekiç.

505
00:45:08.625 --> 00:45:11.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çekici bul, güçlerini geri al.

506
00:45:13.875 --> 00:45:15.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ne yapacağını biliyorsun.

507
00:45:16.750 --> 00:45:18.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ateş nerede?

508
00:45:18.333 --> 00:45:20.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
O konuda endişelenme.

509
00:45:20.208 --> 00:45:22.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Her şey planlandı zaten.
Tek yapman gereken

510
00:45:22.958 --> 00:45:24.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
anahtarı almak.

511
00:45:25.541 --> 00:45:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Onu da kardeşin devlerden almıştı.

512
00:45:29.166 --> 00:45:30.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sonra takımını toplarım.

513
00:45:30.791 --> 00:45:32.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunu yapamam.

514
00:45:32.750 --> 00:45:35.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Neye kullanacağımı bilirse asla vermez.

515
00:45:36.333 --> 00:45:37.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Öyleyse söyleme.

516
00:45:38.750 --> 00:45:42.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Amacın araçları meşru kıldığını
anlaman lazım.

517
00:45:43.583 --> 00:45:46.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Silahı yapıp devleri öldürmezsen

518
00:45:46.458 --> 00:45:48.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
devler seni ve aileni öldürecek.

519
00:45:51.625 --> 00:45:55.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Onu kurtarmak için
ona ihanet mi etmeliyim?

520
00:45:57.000 --> 00:45:58.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen busun.

521
00:45:59.166 --> 00:46:03.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bedeli ne olursa olsun kötülükle savaşan.

522
00:46:03.250 --> 00:46:04.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Evet!
-Evet!

523
00:46:04.791 --> 00:46:06.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Evet!
-Evet!

524
00:46:06.833 --> 00:46:10.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet! Norveç!

525
00:46:11.625 --> 00:46:14.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evet! Norveç! Evet! Norveç!

526
00:46:14.541 --> 00:46:16.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Norveç! Evet!

527
00:46:16.958 --> 00:46:19.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Norveç!

528
00:46:34.166 --> 00:46:35.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Selam.
-Selam.

529
00:46:36.583 --> 00:46:39.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dondurucuda dondurma var istersen.

530
00:46:39.833 --> 00:46:40.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Senin için alırım.

531
00:46:55.041 --> 00:46:56.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Konuşabilir miyiz?

532
00:46:59.041 --> 00:46:59.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kardeşim?

533
00:48:03.583 --> 00:48:08.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
